Create a morse code decoder that does the following when taking an input 'b':
- dot: when the input b in inputted one unit of time
- dash: when input b in inputted for three units of time
-lg: letter gap (3 units of time of doing nothing), this creates a space between letters
- wg: denotes the end of a word (5 units of time of doing nothing), 

